{"tid":2165431,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國軍艦穿越台灣海峽 解放軍未動作","createTime":"2020-08-19T22:24:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T01:45:28.000Z","uid":141151,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8b20b2cdbc7efa33329ba4d3af7cb20dfc2e692c","tid":2165431,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T22:24:47.000Z","msg":"美國軍艦穿越台灣海峽 解放軍未動作<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20200819-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%BB%8D%E8%89%A6%E7%A9%BF%E8%B6%8A%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD-%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E6%9C%AA%E5%8B%95%E4%BD%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20200819-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25BB%258D%25E8%2589%25A6%25E7%25A9%25BF%25E8%25B6%258A%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25B3%25BD-%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%258B%2595%25E4%25BD%259C&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufcpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=7c8a0126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20200819-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%BB%8D%E8%89%A6%E7%A9%BF%E8%B6%8A%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD-%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E6%9C%AA%E5%8B%95%E4%BD%9C</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據中央社今天報道，美艦穿越台灣海峽，解放軍東部戰區指：全程跟監。<br />\n<br />\n根據解放軍東部戰區微信公眾號下午刊登通稿，引述張春暉上述表示，並稱美國近來在涉台問題上&ldquo;消極動作不斷&rdquo;，&ldquo;向台獨勢力發出錯誤信號，嚴重破壞台海和平穩定&rdquo;。張春暉又說，&ldquo;任何破壞&lsquo;一個中國&rsquo;原則、在台海地區滋事攪局的言行，都不符合中美兩國根本利益，損害兩岸同胞共同福祉，給本地區和平穩定帶來現實威脅，是極其危險的&rdquo;。他還說，東部戰區部隊將時刻保持高度戒備，堅決捍衛國家主權和領土完整，堅定維護台海地區和平穩定。<br />\n<br />\n台灣國防部今天則表示，這艘美艦經台灣海峽執行一般航行任務；國軍運用聯合情監偵作為，全程掌握台海周邊海、空域相關動態，狀況正常。<br />\n<br />\n據該消息，美國海軍太平洋艦隊（U.S. Pacific Fleet）今天也罕見在臉書粉絲團公布相關照片，並貼文表示，第7艦隊（U.S. 7th Fleet）勃克級導向飛彈驅逐艦馬斯廷號（USS Mustin, DDG 89）18日航經台灣海峽，圖說指出，馬斯廷號任務為支持印太區域的安全與穩定。第7艦隊新聞稿指出，馬斯廷號與日本海上自衛隊秋月級驅逐艦涼月號（JS Suzutsuki, DD 117）15日在東海舉行綜合演習，作為透過合作共同承擔區域穩定的一環。"},{"pid":"34b6d23d6b192885c5140b15003135f08bdaea09","tid":2165431,"uid":70487,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T22:29:04.000Z","msg":"解褲軍 : 嘩是真的美軍啊～習爹爹你看見嗎？😳"},{"pid":"bd3e497d10a404df6f641c77cf076f7ccea65870","tid":2165431,"uid":337608,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T22:31:24.000Z","msg":"全程跟監 = 雷達work<br />\n今晚領導請飲酒慶祝<br />\n領導飲酒咋<br />\n下面果班飲水"},{"pid":"0072e95e8ff1dfb501fb103df1607ed8b025c83b","tid":2165431,"uid":215876,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T22:33:05.000Z","msg":"可以比咩動作<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />派亞洲第一去囉"},{"pid":"db46f26186a65b4dac76e458daaf6229817b92e6","tid":2165431,"uid":273218,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T22:43:56.000Z","msg":"推美軍行動post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e798345a5bbc92ab7dccf79f23dc458e3249f8","tid":2165431,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T22:44:12.000Z","msg":"推美軍行動post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4bae78d29053c1c72b40bdfe9f714fcff0ed6b0","tid":2165431,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T22:48:22.000Z","msg":"解放軍：我們只會打台軍，不會打美軍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb41d4cb1aa83acb631c46a12500dc668746333","tid":2165431,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db46f26186a65b4dac76e458daaf6229817b92e6","tid":2165431,"uid":273218,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T22:43:56.000Z","msg":"推美軍行動post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T22:58:34.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54938364da9853cceda1b6efb40badd731a60d41","tid":2165431,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T23:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" 